children.subject: I added CS 170 during Phase 1 when I was undeclared and got in with no worries this semester.
Just taking those 3 classes sounds fine to me. You'll be manageably busy.

history.content:
I took both of these classes with DS100 this semester. Others can correct me, but I feel EECS 126 will be difficult to get into without being declared yet. Personally, the workload is definitely manageable as long as you stay on top of problem sets for both of those classes.

------

While it's definitely difficult to get into EECS 126, being declared won't make a difference--with the current enrollment policy there are no reserved seats and anyone can enroll in Phase I.
